column1: # Latitude; decimal_degrees_WGS84; N/A; Manually recorded in metadata from tablet or personal phone.
# Longitude; decimal_degrees_WGS84; N/A; Manually recorded in metadata from tablet or personal phone.
# Temperature; degree_celsius; Minidot_04; PME miniDOT Logger with temperature sensor.
# Dissolved_Oxygen; milligrams_per_liter; Minidot_04; PME miniDOT Logger with optical dissolved oxygen sensor (fluorescence quenching).
# Pressure; millibars; TreeRope_01; In Situ Rugged BaroTROLL 100 ABS with piezoresistive ceramic pressure sensor.
# Pressure; millibars; BaroInterp_01; Calculated from nearby In Situ Rugged BaroTROLL 100 ABS with piezoresistive ceramic pressure sensor pressure sensor corrected for change in elevation.

# Depth; meters; Depth_01; Calculated using (1) In Situ Rugged BaroTROLL 100 ABS with piezoresistive ceramic pressure sensor (2) Onset HOBO water level logger U20L-04 (13 feet) with ceramic pressure sensor and (3) average reach depth.
